Name: Vector Assault
About the game: Vector Assault is a fast paced twin stick shooter where you have to survive a onslaught of enemy attackers. The more enemies you defeat the higher your score will become. Try to achieve the highest score possible across multiple game modes, and levels. Game Features: - Four Game Modes - Arcade - Survival - Weapon Trial - Time Trial - 9 Stages - Multiple Power-ups - 3 Playerable Ships - Challenges/Achievements - Online Leaderboards - Xbox One Controller Support
